Ayuh. Mari bersorak.

363
00:20:31,333 --> 00:20:32,500
sorakan.

364
00:20:32,500 --> 00:20:39,467
[MUZIK LEMBUT DIMAINKAN]

365
00:20:51,367 --> 00:20:52,467
